{% comment %}
  Reusable project detail page for non e-commerce-upgrade cases.
  It intentionally reuses the e-commerce-upgrade visual framework, CSS and JS,
  while templates/page.e-commerce-upgrade.json still points at sections/main-page.liquid unchanged.
